{"tid":1661074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：無意在短期內成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-10-18T01:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T02:18:38.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4c7da7364c87d267bdd9ea82246df8cd22121266","tid":1661074,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:42:53.000Z","msg":"政務司司長張建宗出席一個英文節目表示，昨日呼籲公眾不要再糾纏於7.21元朗西鐵站襲擊事件，是因為監警會已經着手調查近月的示威衝突，包括7.21事件，希望市民給予監警會時間和空間工作，耐心等待在年尾或明年初發表的監警會調查報告。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，特區政府無意在短期內成立獨立調查委員會，直至社會回復正常為止。他又讚揚警方在近期衝突事件中表現非常出色。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，政府會繼續聆聽社會聲音，短期內再次舉行公開的社區對話，亦不希望下月舉行的區議會選舉要延遲。他強調行政長官林鄭月娥缺席《施政報告》電台節目，並非迴避面對公眾。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2278922/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2278922%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=2f438e4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2278922/</a>"},{"pid":"337cb1b053309b50456821781e7f86737fc0a4f2","tid":1661074,"uid":262342,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:43:41.000Z","msg":"比林大總統屌2句就要跪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fff568d308d2e2b24f60a356413a3876ddab08","tid":1661074,"uid":273703,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:44:32.000Z","msg":"拒絕就拒絕啦，咪撚搞語言偽術比假希望啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d15ac10baf4b323c44585ace48adb07151bebfe","tid":1661074,"uid":3765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:44:55.000Z","msg":"你收檔啦 狗官<br />\n<br />\n成個正苦有邊個係有腦<br />\n個個UN UN腳R春袋咁款<br />\n毫無建設性都唔知做過乜<br />\n半樣野都講唔出"},{"pid":"2312b66eb7ffe84694ff99931bd5716d6d3d6336","tid":1661074,"uid":292544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:45:39.000Z","msg":"理9佢up咩 等比人制裁啦"},{"p